cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.HC 

This paper is about personalized recommendation of multimedia items and key frames, which involves techniques from information retrieval (IR), multimedia (MM), machine learning (LG), computer vision (CV), and human-computer interaction (HC). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.MM and cs.LG. cs.CV is also likely because of the use of visual images. Finally, cs.HC is possible because of the focus on user preferences and behavior.
